  "content": {
    "prompt": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">At time <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"t sub 1\"><math alttext=\"t sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>t</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>, a car is traveling to the west with speed <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"v\"><math alttext=\"v\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>v</mi></math></span></span>. At time <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"t sub 2\"><math alttext=\"t sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span>, the car is traveling to the east with speed <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"v\"><math alttext=\"v\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>v</mi></math></span></span>. Which of the following correctly indicates the change in the kinetic energy <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta K\"><math alttext=\"delta K\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Δ</mtext><mi>K</mi></math></span></span> of the car between times <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"t sub 1\"><math alttext=\"t sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>t</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"t sub 2\"><math alttext=\"t sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span>, and provides a valid justification?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i1",
